<div class="problem-page-hdr">
  <div class="prob-icon">📱</div>
  <div>
    <div class="prob-id">基礎問題</div>
    <div class="prob-title-jp">b04　要素数で最強カードを出す</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="problem-body">
<div class="use-vars">
    <div class="use-vars-title">この問題で使うもの</div>
    <span class="var-chip">手札[i]</span>
    <span class="var-chip">要素数[手札]</span>
    <span class="var-chip">出す(値, 枚数)</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-indicator">
